n 3 API path\n  - Verifies the returned object is a `ServiceInfo`\n  - Unadvertises it in a `finally` block\n- Made the existing placeholder top-level test class public to comply with the repository rule:\n  - `Log4j_coreTest.java`\n\nI did not compile or run tests, per instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_049dae7f6ec59baf016a0d8ba75af88193b7093de2d64e607e\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 886, "output": 730, "cacheRead": 22528, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 24144, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1779272600816, "responseId": "resp_049dae7f6ec59baf016a0d8b994c388193af459189bd34ec86"}}
